  "texts": [
    "Pre-training aims to give the model the necessary skills to understand and generate meaningful textual content according to various control codes or signals [103].",
    "Transformer designs similar to BERT [104] and GPT models are used for educational purposes.",
    "A model's predictive ability can be improved through training to analyze statistical patterns in language and grammatical structures to predict the following phrase in a given sentence.",
    "It is essential to perform this task in an organized environment.",
    "An important feature of CTRL is the ability to configure control messages and codes."
  ]
